296
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:31,470
Get up, Ms. Gu.

297
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:32,710
It's Monday.

298
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:36,430
Monday?

299
00:17:36,870 --> 00:17:39,190
I'm calling in sick.

300
00:17:40,950 --> 00:17:42,030
Today is Monday.

301
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:43,790
The day you go to Art List.

302
00:18:07,230 --> 00:18:07,790
Why…

303
00:18:08,630 --> 00:18:10,190
why am I wearing your clothes again?

304
00:18:12,390 --> 00:18:13,230
Don't you remember?

305
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,630
What should I remember?

306
00:18:19,350 --> 00:18:20,030
Ms. Gu,

307
00:18:20,130 --> 00:18:22,190
you know you pounce on people
when you're drunk, right?

308
00:18:23,510 --> 00:18:25,230
And then you ask why
my clothes are on you

309
00:18:25,790 --> 00:18:27,190
when it's you who took them off me.

310
00:18:30,750 --> 00:18:31,550
Me?

311
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:34,070
Took them

312
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:36,630
off you?

313
00:18:49,550 --> 00:18:50,590
Well…

314
00:18:50,910 --> 00:18:51,390
Um…

315
00:18:52,150 --> 00:18:52,550
I'm

316
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:53,670
almost late

317
00:18:53,950 --> 00:18:55,590
for work. I need to wash up.

318
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,640
You really don't remember?

319
00:18:56,710 --> 00:18:57,350
Nope.

320
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:58,670
Should I

321
00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:00,270
remind you?

322
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:04,670
No, no, no need for that…

323
00:19:06,670 --> 00:19:07,390
Liang Daiwen,

324
00:19:08,470 --> 00:19:10,710
you're becoming less like a robot.

325
00:19:11,110 --> 00:19:12,110
Have you evolved?

326
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:13,790
Are you Robot 2.0 now?

327
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:16,190
Isn't evolving good?

328
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:17,990
Evolving…

329
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:20,190
of course it's good.

330
00:19:20,710 --> 00:19:23,670
I enjoy the process of training you.

331
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:25,710
All right.

332
00:19:25,990 --> 00:19:26,670
Then train me.

333
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:28,190
I was joking!

334
00:19:28,190 --> 00:19:29,550
I don't have time to train you.

335
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:30,870
Move. I need to get to work.

336
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:32,370
Now you're suddenly all about work?

337
00:19:32,710 --> 00:19:33,310
All right.

338
00:19:33,830 --> 00:19:34,830
Agree to one condition,

339
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,030
and I'll let you go.

340
00:19:36,430 --> 00:19:36,950
Fine, fine.

341
00:19:37,190 --> 00:19:38,350
What's your condition?

342
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,070
Move back to my place.

343
