♪The mist looms over the streets,
many mysteries are hidden♪

350
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:29,030
♪The stars will guide me♪

351
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:34,560
♪Deep within the noisy crowd,
there is a light♪

352
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:38,110
♪Illuminating me in the darkness♪

353
00:20:38,250 --> 00:20:40,250
♪It should be you♪

354
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:42,900
♪Nobody else but you♪

355
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:45,540
♪A bond formed when we first met♪

356
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:48,460
♪Will lead us into a new journey♪

357
00:20:48,850 --> 00:20:51,080
♪You should be my star♪

358
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,870
♪The moment you cross the sky♪

359
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,370
♪A colorful story is lit♪

360
00:20:56,600 --> 00:21:00,720
♪The wind carries my wish across,
under the gaze of starry skies♪

361
00:21:01,810 --> 00:21:07,180
♪A star flying toward you and I♪

362
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:12,720
♪The rippling galaxy
weaving through my fingertips♪

363
00:21:12,870 --> 00:21:14,440
♪The fireworks reflected
in the skyscrapers♪

364
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:18,190
♪Distant,
yet nurturing my beautiful dreams♪

365
00:21:18,410 --> 00:21:21,680
♪So when I wake, I don't fall♪

366
00:21:21,930 --> 00:21:23,760
♪It should be you♪

367
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:26,320
♪Nobody else but you♪

368
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:29,170
♪A colorful story is lit♪

369
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:32,760
♪The wind carries my wish across,
under the gaze of starry skies♪

370
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:35,920
(Art List New Media Center)

371
00:21:36,070 --> 00:21:36,630
Ms. Gu,

372
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,750
is there anything else you need from me?

373
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:41,070
No, everything's done.

374
00:21:41,110 --> 00:21:42,230
All right, I'm heading home then.

375
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:43,350
Okay, head back early.

376
00:21:43,350 --> 00:21:43,710
Okay.

377
00:21:43,710 --> 00:21:45,070
You too.

378
00:21:45,190 --> 00:21:45,550
Bye.

379
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:46,110
Bye.

380
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:18,040
(Video call from Robot)

381
00:22:23,860 --> 00:22:25,860
(Robot)

382
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:30,830
What are you doing?

383
00:22:31,630 --> 00:22:32,790
Buying daily necessities.

384
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:33,630
Take a look.

385
00:22:33,730 --> 00:22:34,790
Do you need any of these?

386
00:22:39,470 --> 00:22:40,750
Anything's fine.

387
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:44,470
Do you really need to be
so indecisive about stuff like this?

388
00:22:46,230 --> 00:22:46,630
Got it.

389
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:48,190
I'll buy one of each.

390
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:51,030
Anything you want to eat?

391
00:22:51,750 --> 00:22:52,390
Liang Daiwen,

392
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,470
why don't you just buy
a wedding decoration

393
00:22:54,500 --> 00:22:55,630
for the door while you're at it?

394
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:56,870
Comedic setup.

395
00:22:59,030 --> 00:22:59,750
Okay, stop teasing.

396
00:22:59,870 --> 00:23:00,590
Hurry home.

397
00:23:00,760 --> 00:23:02,430
If I need anything,
I'll just buy it online.

398
00:23:03,630 --> 00:23:04,670
When do you get off work?

399
00:23:04,710 --> 00:23:05,620
I'll come pick you up.

400
00:23:07,270 --> 00:23:07,670
No need.

401
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:11,030
I want to go back to my old place
to grab a few things.

402
00:23:11,430 --> 00:23:12,390
I'll handle it myself.

403
00:23:12,450 --> 00:23:14,230
I've already moved
all your stuff from there.

404
00:23:14,390 --> 00:23:15,110
What else do you need?

405
00:23:17,270 --> 00:23:19,070
Something important.

406
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:20,550
Just go home.

407
00:23:20,910 --> 00:23:21,390
Bye.

408
00:23:33,950 --> 00:23:34,430
Gu Yi!

409
00:23:35,190 --> 00:23:35,750
Gu Yi!

410
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:41,030
Where's Gu Yi?

411
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:42,390
Are you looking for Ms. Yi, Ms. Zhang?

412
00:23:42,510 --> 00:23:44,310
She's reporting in at Art List today.

413
00:23:47,390 --> 00:23:47,950
I forgot.

414
00:23:48,390 --> 00:23:49,890
You should hurry and get off work.

415
00:24:05,990 --> 00:24:06,550
Mr. Huang.

416
00:24:06,770 --> 00:24:07,720
Where's Zhang Junjie?

417
00:24:08,070 --> 00:24:08,630
She's inside.

418
00:24:22,560 --> 00:24:23,790
If you have something to say, say it.

419
00:24:24,150 --> 00:24:24,750
If not, leave.

420
00:24:27,190 --> 00:24:28,750
You're being so dismissive today.

421
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:30,870
What happened
to your company's Biluochun tea?

422
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:42,310
No need to be impatient.

423
00:24:42,690 --> 00:24:43,910
I'm heading back to Beijing soon.

424
00:24:44,070 --> 00:24:45,910
I just came by to say goodbye.

425
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:50,950
Everything settled with Guan Xingxin?

426
00:24:53,630 --> 00:24:55,110
After that show,

427
00:24:55,270 --> 00:24:57,030
a lot of companies wanted to sign her,

428
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:58,470
but she turned them all down.

429
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:00,550
I can't keep focusing on an artist

430
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:01,990
who doesn't want to progress, can I?

431
00:25:03,430 --> 00:25:04,590
Her future is up

432
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:05,950
to her.

433
00:25:10,070 --> 00:25:10,830
Be honest.

434
00:25:23,710 --> 00:25:24,630
It's nothing major.

435
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:25,710
At the celebration party,

436
00:25:26,190 --> 00:25:26,990
an advertiser

437
00:25:27,870 --> 00:25:29,430
said something inappropriate,

438
00:25:29,430 --> 00:25:30,310
and I punched them.

439
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:33,470
They've been pestering me
these past few days,

440
00:25:33,470 --> 00:25:34,150
and I'm fed up.

441
00:25:34,450 --> 00:25:36,160
Heading back to Beijing
for some peace and quiet.

442
00:25:37,030 --> 00:25:38,070
You're a grown adult.

443
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:40,030
Can't you think before you act?

444
00:25:40,630 --> 00:25:42,150
They deserved it.

445
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:48,710
But

446
00:25:49,910 --> 00:25:51,830
when I hit them, I felt like

447
00:25:53,470 --> 00:25:55,230
I was hitting my younger self.

448
00:25:58,020 --> 00:26:00,280
Do you still remember
what happened to us back then?

449
00:26:01,250 --> 00:26:02,240
I've forgotten.

450
00:26:05,390 --> 00:26:05,710
Good.

451
00:26:06,720 --> 00:26:07,780
It's better forgotten.

452
00:26:09,910 --> 00:26:10,950
I still remember

453
00:26:11,630 --> 00:26:13,190
the year I brought you to Donghai.

454
00:26:13,190 --> 00:26:14,640
There wasn't even a high-speed rail yet.

455
00:26:15,110 --> 00:26:16,910
We took a hard sleeper train.

456
00:26:17,430 --> 00:26:18,430
It was an eight-hour ride,

457
00:26:18,430 --> 00:26:19,670
and my back was killing me.

458
00:26:21,750 --> 00:26:22,390
You

459
00:26:22,790 --> 00:26:23,670
sat

460
00:26:24,070 --> 00:26:25,510
in the train corridor,

461
00:26:26,270 --> 00:26:27,110
staring out the window,

462
00:26:28,230 --> 00:26:29,550
and looking so excited.

463
00:26:30,470 --> 00:26:31,870
Like you'd never seen the world.

464
00:26:35,630 --> 00:26:37,070
Looking at you,

465
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:40,270
I thought it was endearing.

466
00:26:45,830 --> 00:26:46,630
Later,

467
00:26:48,150 --> 00:26:49,630
you fell out with your family
because of me.

468
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:52,590
After that,

469
00:26:53,310 --> 00:26:54,710
when my career stabilized

470
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:57,510
and I started making money,

471
00:26:58,870 --> 00:26:59,870
I wanted to get married.

472
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:03,670
Half of it was for myself,

473
00:27:04,750 --> 00:27:05,790
but the other half

474
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:07,310
was out of care for you.

475
00:27:08,910 --> 00:27:10,110
That's what I thought back then.

476
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:11,390
I thought,

477
00:27:12,310 --> 00:27:13,750
if we keep working ourselves

478
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:15,590
into the ground
and end up in the hospital,

479
00:27:16,430 --> 00:27:17,230
what's the point?

480
00:27:17,950 --> 00:27:18,870
It's not worth it.

481
00:27:19,550 --> 00:27:20,470
So I thought,

482
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:22,500
I'd go out and earn money,
and you could stay home

483
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:25,170
and take care of the family.
Wouldn't that be great?

484
00:27:26,830 --> 00:27:27,750
But

485
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:30,910
I didn't expect you to refuse.

486
00:27:32,110 --> 00:27:33,910
Whenever we talked about it,

487
00:27:33,910 --> 00:27:35,470
we'd fight.

488
00:27:35,630 --> 00:27:36,390
Fight until…

489
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:45,270
You know,

490
00:27:47,230 --> 00:27:48,590
when I heard
you were pregnant back then,

491
00:27:50,630 --> 00:27:51,870
I was so happy.

492
00:27:59,190 --> 00:27:59,670
I know.

493
00:28:01,030 --> 00:28:02,870
You don't want
to hear this old story again,

494
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:05,630
but I remember it all.

495
00:28:07,430 --> 00:28:08,430
And I don't plan to forget.

496
00:28:11,870 --> 00:28:13,110
Over the years,

497
00:28:14,430 --> 00:28:15,830
Donghai has always been
a sad place for me.

498
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:19,510
I've loved you,

499
00:28:21,510 --> 00:28:22,230
and I've resented you.

500
00:28:24,190 --> 00:28:25,710
Even now,

501
00:28:28,430 --> 00:28:29,510
I can't let you go.

502
00:28:31,110 --> 00:28:32,390
You've become my inner demon.

503
00:28:43,470 --> 00:28:43,950
All right.

504
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:46,150
I've said everything I wanted to.

505
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,110
I feel better now.

506
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:49,990
I won't bring it up again.

507
00:28:54,950 --> 00:28:55,510
Junjie.

508
00:28:58,590 --> 00:28:59,470
Can we let go

509
00:29:00,830 --> 00:29:01,910
of all the grudges

510
00:29:03,110 --> 00:29:04,750
from the past

511
00:29:05,830 --> 00:29:06,430
and start over?

512
00:29:07,630 --> 00:29:08,070
Can we

513
00:29:09,470 --> 00:29:09,870
move on?

514
00:29:16,950 --> 00:29:17,550
I know.

515
00:29:20,590 --> 00:29:22,110
I still owe you an apology.

516
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:28,350
Zhang Junjie,

517
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,470
you're the best woman

518
00:29:34,910 --> 00:29:35,910
I've ever known.

519
00:29:40,670 --> 00:29:42,230
I shouldn't have
disrespected you back then.

520
00:29:43,390 --> 00:29:44,830
I shouldn't have tried

521
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:47,790
to control your life,

522
00:29:51,390 --> 00:29:52,110
forcing you to…

523
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,230
Forcing you

524
00:29:59,990 --> 00:30:01,230
to have an abortion

525
00:30:02,870 --> 00:30:03,830
just to escape from me.

526
00:30:14,070 --> 00:30:14,670
I'm sorry.

527
00:30:17,670 --> 00:30:18,150
I mean it.

528
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:21,270
I'm sorry.

529
00:31:49,590 --> 00:31:50,270
Mom,

530
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:53,470
I'm moving.

531
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:50,900
(Happy Marriage)

532
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:17,910
Liang Daiwen!

533
00:33:20,430 --> 00:33:22,110
What's with the wedding decoration
at the door?

534
00:33:23,430 --> 00:33:24,870
Didn't you ask me to buy it?

535
00:33:25,090 --> 00:33:26,680
The supermarkets were sold out.

536
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:28,430
I had to go
to several gift shops to find it.

537
00:33:29,590 --> 00:33:30,910
Take it down!

538
00:33:32,830 --> 00:33:33,270
No.

539
00:33:34,230 --> 00:33:35,190
You won't?

540
00:33:35,630 --> 00:33:36,390
Then, I will.

541
00:33:37,250 --> 00:33:39,170
You tear it down, and I'll buy another.

542
00:34:09,200 --> 00:34:12,420
(Be Happy Everyday)

543
00:34:19,870 --> 00:34:21,030
You spent the whole day

544
00:34:21,910 --> 00:34:23,030
on this?

545
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:26,590
The robot and cat drawings

546
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:28,190
are copied
from that long comic of yours.

547
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:30,040
Didn't need much imagination,

548
00:34:30,510 --> 00:34:31,430
so they were easier to draw.

549
00:34:36,110 --> 00:34:38,470
What about the one
in your bedroom?

550
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:41,230
That one? No one.

551
00:34:41,990 --> 00:34:42,790
It's of my home.

552
00:34:44,910 --> 00:34:46,150
When my mom was sick,

553
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:47,550
she often stared outside

554
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:48,910
through that window.

555
00:34:50,950 --> 00:34:51,750
For some reason,

556
00:34:53,430 --> 00:34:54,510
I always think of that image.

557
00:35:40,630 --> 00:35:42,390
You woke up happy today.

558
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:45,510
Because I realized

559
00:35:46,270 --> 00:35:48,070
that from now on,

560
00:35:48,630 --> 00:35:50,270
the first thing I'll see
every morning is you.

561
00:35:51,270 --> 00:35:52,350
That makes me very happy.

562
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:58,070
Your bar for happiness is pretty low.

563
00:36:03,470 --> 00:36:05,630
It's enough for me.

564
00:36:07,110 --> 00:36:07,790
Don't worry.

565
00:36:09,590 --> 00:36:11,550
I won't casually propose again.

566
00:36:35,910 --> 00:36:36,910
(Art List)

567
00:36:39,270 --> 00:36:41,790
When discussing gender topics,
the entry point must be sharp,

568
00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:43,750
but avoid being inflammatory.

569
00:36:44,470 --> 00:36:46,270
For topics like advice from 30-year-olds

570
00:36:46,270 --> 00:36:47,230
to 20-year-olds,

571
00:36:47,230 --> 00:36:48,910
we've done this

572
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:50,390
countless times

573
00:36:50,390 --> 00:36:51,750
when I was at Nextmonday.

574
00:36:52,310 --> 00:36:54,150
